      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy testing for the hemolysis transport equation demonstrated on canonical benchmark; manufactured solution verification completed.",
      "rationale": "Code verification was performed for the Navier-Stokes solver via the method of manufactured solutions, but the power-law hemolysis damage accumulation equation was not subjected to equivalent order-of-accuracy testing. Gap persists at MRL 5."
