      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study performed; GCI for pressure rise is 3.2%, satisfying hydraulic requirements. GCI for hemolysis index is 11.4%, exceeding the 5% threshold. Achieved level 3 is insufficient for required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
