      "rationale": "FDA pump experiments used bovine blood at fixed hematocrit; VAD clinical hematocrit range (25–45%) and patient-specific anticoagulation protocols are not represented. Temperature variation across operating envelope not controlled. Achieved level 3 is two gradations below required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
