      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative agreement metric (e.g., E% or U95 coverage) applied to hemolysis index predictions at all 5 operating points; comparison accounts for experimental uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative trend agreement is demonstrated but quantitative error metrics incorporating experimental uncertainty bands are not reported for hemolysis index. Systematic over-prediction at high-shear points is noted without formal metric. Achieved level 2 is far below required level 5."
    },
