      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which shares topological features with the target VAD but differs in impeller diameter and volute design. Operating regime partially overlaps COU envelope. Extrapolation risk is unquantified. Achieved level 3 insufficient for required level 5."
    },
