      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation execution procedure with independent analyst review; checklist-based QA for boundary condition setup and post-processing of hemolysis index.",
      "rationale": "No formal use-error assessment was performed. Simulation execution relied on a single analyst without independent review of boundary condition assignments or post-processing scripts. Epistemic gap flagged at MRL 5."
    },
