      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification of power-law hemolysis model form including literature basis, applicability range, and known failure modes; alternative model forms evaluated.",
      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model is used without formal model-form justification. No alternative hemolysis model forms (e.g., strain-based, energy dissipation-based) were evaluated. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
