      "acceptanceCriteria": "All hemolysis model input parameters (power-law coefficients, blood viscosity, hematocrit) characterized with probability distributions; Monte Carlo propagation completed and reported with full traceability.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed propagating uncertainty in flow boundary conditions, but hemolysis model coefficients (alpha, beta, C) were treated as fixed nominal values without uncertainty characterization. Input uncertainty for blood rheological properties is also unquantified. Partial UQ does not satisfy MRL 5 requirements."
    },
